486
00:35:58,800 --> 00:35:59,869
I was lied to...

487
00:36:00,160 --> 00:36:03,436
about the consequences of my liposuction.

488
00:36:03,760 --> 00:36:06,149
I have bumps all over my stomach.

489
00:36:07,000 --> 00:36:08,513
And what happened to you?

490
00:36:09,080 --> 00:36:13,471
I was attacked in my home by a man
who raped me and carved up my face.

491
00:36:19,920 --> 00:36:21,592
How can you violate this girl again?

492
00:36:21,760 --> 00:36:24,672
BOBBl: Hasn't she suffered enough?
NAOMl: What are you talking about?

493
00:36:24,840 --> 00:36:27,274
Dr. McNamara fixed my face...

494
00:36:27,760 --> 00:36:29,637
and he probably saved my career.

495
00:36:32,400 --> 00:36:34,675
