496
00:36:34,840 --> 00:36:35,909
NAOMl: Lady, hold on.

497
00:36:36,560 --> 00:36:38,073
You are not a victim.

498
00:36:39,160 --> 00:36:42,550
Next time you look in the mirror
at your flat stomach that you paid for...

499
00:36:42,720 --> 00:36:46,076
