501
00:36:57,880 --> 00:36:59,108
Now I'm pressing charges.

502
00:36:59,280 --> 00:37:02,078
Did I really walk into her room
and compare her story to mine?

503
00:37:02,240 --> 00:37:04,435
I understand why they didn't hire you.
You're crazy.

504
00:37:04,600 --> 00:37:07,398
