because I didn't show up for the interview!

505
00:37:08,720 --> 00:37:09,869
I chickened out.

506
00:37:10,480 --> 00:37:13,358
It wasn't your bad lipo job, it was me.

507
00:37:14,880 --> 00:37:16,916
I did everything
that you told me not to do.

508
00:37:17,960 --> 00:37:20,110
I overate. I didn't exercise.

509
00:37:23,120 --> 00:37:24,599
I did this to myself.

510
00:37:26,240 --> 00:37:28,800
That way I could blame it
on everybody else...

511
00:37:31,200 --> 00:37:32,315
except myself.

512
00:37:52,280 --> 00:37:53,395
Why?

513
00:37:57,840 --> 00:38:01,958
They were never gonna hire me
to be a personal shopper.

514
00:38:05,040 --> 00:38:06,996
I didn't have the experience.

515
00:38:08,920 --> 00:38:11,115
All I really wanted
was for somebody to say:

516
00:38:13,480 --> 00:38:14,993
"What do you think, Bobbi?"

517
00:38:17,680 --> 00:38:19,193
I just wanted to matter again.

518
00:38:21,880 --> 00:38:24,030
I didn't realize
you were under so much stress.

519
00:38:26,520 --> 00:38:27,555
I'm sorry.

520
00:38:28,720 --> 00:38:31,439
I could have explained
about your recovery a little better.

521
00:38:33,840 --> 00:38:35,432
I'm sorry about the meat thing.

522
00:38:36,680 --> 00:38:38,033
It was really wrong.

523
00:38:40,840 --> 00:38:43,832
We usually give all our potential clients
a list of references...

524
00:38:44,000 --> 00:38:45,831
before they schedule any surgery.

525
00:38:47,000 --> 00:38:50,675
If you'd be open to it, I'd like to add you
to the list for them to call.

526
00:38:51,080 --> 00:38:52,832
You'd use me as a reference now?

527
00:38:53,600 --> 00:38:57,195
I mean, my liposuction was a disaster...

528
00:39:00,080 --> 00:39:02,640
- and I couldn't lie about that.
- I don't want you to.

529
00:39:04,240 --> 00:39:07,710
A "con" point of view might be
a nice and necessary perspective.

530
00:39:10,560 --> 00:39:14,030
It'd also give you a chance to hear
someone ask, "What do you think, Bobbi?"

531
00:39:19,760 --> 00:39:21,193
I wanna break up with you.

532
00:39:27,160 --> 00:39:29,913
Matt, don't allow fear to destroy
the good in your life.

533
00:39:30,320 --> 00:39:31,833
I'm not changing my mind.

534
00:39:32,040 --> 00:39:35,510
I just wanted to be a man,
and come over and tell you to your face.

535
00:39:35,680 --> 00:39:39,070
Be a man? Okay, I can respect that.

536
00:39:40,080 --> 00:39:42,116
If you're so grown up then, explain to me...

537
00:39:42,280 --> 00:39:44,555
why you feel we can't
continue this relationship.

538
00:39:45,640 --> 00:39:49,349
I can't keep going around
and lying to everyone.

539
00:39:51,320 --> 00:39:52,389
I'm done.

540
00:40:03,360 --> 00:40:05,749
The last thing I wanna do
is cause you more pain.

541
00:40:08,560 --> 00:40:13,076
But through my professional experience,
I can see what you don't.

542
00:40:14,280 --> 00:40:16,316
Your mother is the duplicitous one,
not you.

543
00:40:16,480 --> 00:40:19,870
Why would you say that?
You don't know her at all.

544
00:40:21,680 --> 00:40:25,878
These unexplained,
subconscious feelings of conflict...

545
00:40:26,040 --> 00:40:30,113
bubbling up to the surface
and causing painful exterior drama...

546
00:40:31,920 --> 00:40:34,275
are completely explainable.

547
00:40:34,720 --> 00:40:36,438
They are not your fault.

548
00:40:37,080 --> 00:40:40,959
When you've been cruelly denied
the truth about the core of your identity...

549
00:40:41,440 --> 00:40:43,078
how could you not have doubt?

550
00:40:43,920 --> 00:40:46,275
My identity is fine, Ava.

551
00:40:48,760 --> 00:40:53,515
Your identity is predicated on a lie,
perpetuated by your mother.

552
00:41:05,920 --> 00:41:07,717
What are you doing in my room?

553
00:41:09,040 --> 00:41:11,110
Something I should
have done a long time ago.

554
00:41:11,520 --> 00:41:14,557
Finding out what the hell
is going on in my son's life.

555
00:41:14,720 --> 00:41:15,994
By going through my stuff?

556
00:41:16,160 --> 00:41:19,072
From now on, you'll have to earn
your privacy in this house.

557
00:41:19,600 --> 00:41:21,716
There are gonna be
no more secrets between us.

558
00:41:21,880 --> 00:41:24,394
Why don't we start by the one
you're keeping from me?

559
00:41:25,080 --> 00:41:28,072
- What are you talking about?
- Ava told me.

560
00:41:29,400 --> 00:41:32,358
You've been lying to me,
my whole life, about who I am.

561
00:41:32,520 --> 00:41:36,479
Ava is a manipulator, Matt. You cannot
believe anything she tells you.

562
00:41:36,720 --> 00:41:38,392
Christian's my real dad, isn't he?

563
00:41:42,040 --> 00:41:43,314
What?

564
00:41:45,000 --> 00:41:46,672
That's crazy.

565
00:41:46,840 --> 00:41:49,912
I've seen the way you two look
at each other, how close you are.

566
00:41:50,080 --> 00:41:52,071
He even said he thinks of me as a son.

567
00:41:54,480 --> 00:41:58,996
If you want me to be honest with you
about my life, then tell me the truth.

568
00:42:02,360 --> 00:42:04,078
Is Christian...

569
00:42:06,200 --> 00:42:07,394
my real father?

570
00:42:11,000 --> 00:42:11,989
Tell me!

571
00:42:20,200 --> 00:42:21,315
Yes.

572
00:42:26,720 --> 00:42:30,030
I didn't know for the longest time.

573
00:42:30,760 --> 00:42:32,557
Matt, I'm so sorry.

574
00:42:33,600 --> 00:42:35,909
I didn't know what to do. We're a family.

575
00:42:36,080 --> 00:42:39,709
No, this whole family is bullshit,
and you're the reason why.

576
00:42:39,880 --> 00:42:42,553
Don't talk to me like that.
I am still your mother!

577
00:42:42,760 --> 00:42:44,716
You're not my mother. You're a whore.

578
00:42:46,040 --> 00:42:49,032
Even if you did hit me,
it would still be true.

579
00:42:49,880 --> 00:42:52,269
Matt, I am so sorry.

580
00:42:55,800 --> 00:42:57,233
You have to understand...

581
00:42:57,840 --> 00:43:00,673
none of this changes
the way that I feel about you...

582
00:43:02,080 --> 00:43:03,877
the way your dad feels about you.

583
00:43:04,040 --> 00:43:08,716
Does he even know, or have you been
lying to him this whole time, too?

584
00:43:09,200 --> 00:43:10,394
About what?

585
00:43:14,960 --> 00:43:17,394
Lying about what?
What the hell's going on here?

586
00:43:24,360 --> 00:43:25,554
Ava...

587
00:43:28,240 --> 00:43:29,992
and I have been seeing each other.

588
00:43:31,120 --> 00:43:32,235
We slept together.

589
00:43:32,400 --> 00:43:34,595
What? Since when?

590
00:43:36,040 --> 00:43:37,632
You just found out about this?

591
00:43:39,480 --> 00:43:40,629
It's over.

592
00:43:45,640 --> 00:43:46,595
Dad.

593
00:43:53,360 --> 00:43:56,193
Hey, it's okay, Matt.

594
00:43:59,000 --> 00:44:00,228
